\ Problem 3
\ 
\ Write a definition that "rings" your terminal's bell three times. Make sure that 
\ there is enough of a delay between the bells so that they are distinguishable. 
\ Each time the bell rings, the word "BEEP" should appear on the terminal screen.

: verbose-bell
	bell ." BEEP" cr ;


: rings ( n --)
	0 do bell loop ;

3 rings
